    v2 = 0.07
    tmp = ((0.39 / (v2 + 0.68 / v2 + 0.80)) * ((tmp + 0.54 + v2 + 0.39) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.90)))
    v1 = ((v2 / wp.sin(v0 + 0.71)) / wp.cos(0.21))
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
